<LI>Telephone interview by FRC Research Assistant Daniel Garcia with Steve Cherrington of NEH's Office of Planning 
and Budget on May 18, 1995.  
<LI>Jennifer A. Marshall and Eric Unsworth, "Faulty Standards," in "Freeing America's Schools,"<I> Family Policy</I>, 
Family Research Council, April 1995, p. 5.
<LI>See, for instance, <I>The National Endowments: A Critical Symposium</I>, Center for the Study of Popular Culture, 
Laurence Jarvik, Herbert I. London and James F. Cooper, editors, 1995, pp. 1-52.
</OL></FONT>

