http://www.empower.org:80/townhall/columnists/buckley/buck022796.html 204.71.237.79 19970210082142 text/html 5626
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 10-Feb-97 08:22:27 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 31-May-96 20:06:56 GMT
Content-length: 5443
