http://www.empower.org:80/wash_times/fields.8-11.html 204.71.237.79 19970210084152 text/html 5569
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 10-Feb-97 08:42:38 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 05-Aug-96 13:50:34 GMT
