<head>
<title>Columnist Kathleen Howley</title>
</head>

<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/townhall/background.jpg">

<center>




<h2>Town Hall Guest Columnist<p>
Kathleen Howley</h2>

</center>


<h5><a href="/townhall/columnists/i-howley.html.cgi">[Graphics On]</a></h5>
<hr size="3" width="60%">








<p>






<a href="/townhall/columnists/howley.html"><b>Biography</b></a>
<UL>
<li>March 26, 1996 <a href="/townhall/columnists/howley/howl032296.html">The American President</a>
<li>March 12, 1996 <a href="/townhall/columnists/howley/howl030896.html">Men & Abortion</a>
<li>December 8, 1995 <a href="/townhall/columnists/howley/howl120795.html">Laughter:  The Best Medicine</a>
<li>November 28, 1995 <a href="/townhall/columnists/howley/howl112895.html">Divorce, Irish Style</a>
<li>November 16, 1995 <a href="/townhall/columnists/howley/howl111695.html">Pagans I Have Known</a>
<li>November 7, 1995 <a href="/townhall/columnists/howley/howl110795.html">The Catholic Church(es) In China</a>
<li>October 18, 1995 <a href="/townhall/columnists/howley/howl101895.html">Old TV Makes A Comeback</a>
