<html>

<head>
<title>Columnist William W. Pascoe, III</title>
</head>


<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/townhall/background.jpg">

<center>




<h2>Town Hall Guest Columnist<p>
William W. Pascoe, III</h2>


</center>


<h5><a href="/townhall/columnists/i-pascoe.html.cgi">[Graphics On]</a></h5>
<hr size="3" width="60%">








<p>

<!insert photo here>

<a href="/townhall/columnists/pascoe.html"><b>Biography</b></a>
<UL>
<li>January 24, 1997 <a href="/conservative/columnists/pasc012497.html">Ideology or Partisanship for the GOP?</a>
<li>June 5, 1996 <a href="/conservative/columnists/pasc0605.html">Conservatives Stuck In The Past?</a>
<li>December 22, 1995 <a href="/conservative/columnists/pasc1223.html">Jockeying for the Cultural Conservatives</a>
<li>December 22, 1995 <a href="/conservative/columnists/pasc1222.html">No Taxpayer-Paid Vacations for Furloughed Federal Employees</a>
<li>December 22, 1995 <a href="/conservative/columnists/pasc1221.html">Dole Reverses Field, Saves Himself ...For Now</a>
<li>December 20, 1995 <a href="/conservative/columnists/pasc1220.html">Nuts! to Iowa and New Hampshire</a>
<li>August 29, 1995 <a href="/townhall/columnists/gramm.html">
Gramm: Candidate For The New Environment</a>
<li>August 29, 1995 <a href="/townhall/columnists/bradley.html">Bradley To
Reelect Clinton?</a>
<P><a href="/conservative/i-col.html">Archive</a>
</ul>
<p><br><p><br>








<center>

<center>
<a href="/index/issues.html.cgi/textonly"><i>Issues</i></a> | <a href="/index/improved/welcome.html.cgi/textonly"><i>Search</i></a> | <a href="/townhall/whats_new/welcome.html.cgi/textonly"><i>What's New</i></a> | <a href="/townhall/spotlights/welcome.html.cgi/textonly"><i>TH Spotlights</i></a> | <a href="/townhall/wgw-forum/ac/dispatch.cgi/"><i>Discussions</i></a><br>

