<html>

<head>
<title>Columnist Thomas Schatz</title>
</head>


<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/townhall/background.jpg">

<center>




<h2>Town Hall Guest Columnist<p>
Thomas Schatz</h2>


</center>


<h5><a href="/townhall/columnists/i-schatz.html.cgi">[Graphics On]</a></h5>
<hr size="3" width="60%">








<p>






<a href="/townhall/columnists/schatz.html"><b>Biography</b></a>
<UL>
<li>August 2, 1996 <a href="/townhall/columnists/schatz/scha080296.html">
Why the District Is Different</a>
<li>August 1, 1996 <a href="/townhall/columnists/schatz/scha080196.html">
Radioactive Tax Boondoggle</a>
<li>December 21, 1995 <a href="/townhall/columnists/schatz/scha122195.html">Finders Keepers</a>
<li>November 13, 1995 <a href="/townhall/columnists/schatz/scha111395.html">No Virginia, there is no Budget in Washington</a>
<li>August 28, 1995 <a href = "/townhall/columnists/schatz/scha082595.html">Tales From The Gypped</a>
<li>August 8, 1995 <a href = "/townhall/columnists/schatz/scha072795.html">Red, Red Whine</a>
<LI>July 28, 1995 <A HREF = "/townhall/columnists/schatz/scha070695.html">HUD: Back To The Drawing
Board</A>
<p><a href="/townhall/columnists/schatz/">Archive</a>
</ul>
<p>








